Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:02.47,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnJPORPL7C\bord2\blur4\pos(960,880)}会的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:37.16,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Something is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:39.83,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}A story is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:42.46,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Do you like it?  Do you hate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:45.13,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Got any doubts? I don't think so. Let's jump into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:47.63,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}C-C-Come and kick up! Are you ready ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:50.47,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}C-C-Come and kick up! Now let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.47,0:01:53.18,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}C-C-Come and kick up! Are you ready ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:55.76,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}C-C-Come and kick up! Now let'sgo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:59.81,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Bounce, 高鳴る鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.81,0:02:02.52,OP - JP,,1000,0,0,,{\blur4}No doubts, 感じる波動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:04.65,OP - JP,,1000,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}研ぎ澄ます感性をCONTROL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:06.73,OP - JP,,800,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Like a 歌舞伎的 Playing a role.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:07.94,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}When you're in trouble, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:09.98,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What's a Hero? Break the old ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:12.53,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}What's a Hero? Make new waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:15.20,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}That's a hero! Save all the days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:18.41,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}You can be who you are & be free yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:20.58,OP - JP,,600,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}Is this where it ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:22.87,OP - JP,,600,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}No no 終わらない Broken road
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:23.50,OP - JP,,600,0,0,,{\blur4}続くStory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:26.33,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}信じるのは　自分のHEART
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.13,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大義より仁義　異論はなし
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:29.30,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}BELIEVE IN YOURSELF
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:32.17,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}背負った誓い　歪ませない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.55,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}巻き起こせ　革命REVOLUTION
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:37.64,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}挑め世界　沈ませない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:40.35,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}舞い上がる　異端NO IMITATION
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.98,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}YOU AND I FEEL ALIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:46.35,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}Overdrive It's all right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:49.19,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}誰がヒーロー？ Break the old ways
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.69,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}お前がヒーロー！ MAKE NEW WAVES
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.32,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}C-C-Come and kick up! Are you ready ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:57.07,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}C-C-Come and kick up! Now let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:59.91,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}C-C-Come and kick up! Are you ready ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:01.95,OP - JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,200)}C-C-Come and kick up! NOW LET'S GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:37.16,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是什么悄然而至
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:39.83,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}传奇即将拉开序幕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:42.46,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你会喜不自胜还是鄙夷不屑？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:45.13,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}亦或者犹豫不决？ 而我心意已决  共赴这传奇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:47.63,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.63,0:01:50.47,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！即刻出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.47,0:01:53.18,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:55.76,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！即刻出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:59.81,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}心潮澎湃  热血沸腾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.81,0:02:02.52,OP - CN,,0,1000,0,,{\blur4}毋庸置疑  感受波动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:04.65,OP - CN,,0,1000,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}控制好敏锐的感性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:06.73,OP - CN,,0,800,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}像歌舞伎那般演绎自我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:07.94,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}当你深陷泥潭  是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:09.98,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}何为英雄？ 革旧鼎新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:12.53,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}何为英雄？ 独领风骚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:15.20,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是英雄！ 救民济世
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:18.41,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你大可率性而为  逍遥自在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:20.58,OP - CN,,600,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}可这就是英雄的终点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:22.87,OP - CN,,600,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}不  艰难险阻永无止尽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:23.50,OP - CN,,600,0,0,,{\blur4}传奇还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:26.33,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}坚守本心  矢志不移
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.13,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}仁义高于大义  无可辩驳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:29.30,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:32.17,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}一言九鼎  驷马难追
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.55,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}揭竿而起  掀起革命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:37.64,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(0,400)}挑战世界  宁死不屈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:40.35,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}展翅高飞  去做那绝无仅有的异端
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.98,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}感受彼此生命的共振
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:46.35,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,0)}放手一搏  全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:49.19,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}何为英雄？ 革旧鼎新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.69,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你是英雄！ 独领风骚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:54.32,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:57.07,OP - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来-来-来兴风作浪吧！即刻出发！
